ed="T" n="0748a25"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0748a25"/><head><date from-iso="+0923-05-18" key="j20583162063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16">後唐</date><placeName key="PL000000023652">洛京長壽寺</placeName><persName key="A009905">可止</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0748a26"/><persName key="A009905">釋可止</persName>，姓馬氏，<placeName key="PL000000000446">范陽大房山高丘</placeName>人也。年甫<lb
ed="T" n="0748a27"/><date key="j20391872039551" from-iso="+0871-01-01" to-iso="+0871-12-31">十二</date>，逈有出俗之心，依<placeName key="PL000000000351">憫忠寺</placeName><persName key="A009906">法貞律師</persName>。<date key="j20402832040647" from-iso="+0874-01-01" to-iso="+0874-12-31">年<lb
ed="T" n="0748a28"/>十五</date>，為息慈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g964"/>，辭<ref type="person" target="#A009906">師</ref>往<placeName key="PL000000000866">真定</placeName>習學經論。時<placeName key="PL000000005362">大<lb
ed="T" n="0748a29"/>華嚴寺</placeName>有<persName key="A009908">仁楚法師</persName>講《因明論》，<persName key="A009905">止</persName>執卷服<pb ed="T" n="0748b" xml:id="T50.2061.0748b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0748b01"/>膺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1119"/>三遍，精義<ptr target="#n1106"/>入神，眾推俊邁。有老宿<persName key="A009918">維摩<lb
ed="T" n="0748b02"/>和尚</persName>者，釋門之奇士也，問<ref type="person" target="#A009908">楚師</ref>曰：「門人秀<lb
ed="T" n="0748b03"/>拔，孰者為先？」曰：「有<placeName key="PL000000000368">幽州</placeName>沙彌者，溫故知新<ptr target="#n1120"/><lb
ed="T" n="0748b04"/>厲精弗懈。」於是求見，遂質問<persName key="A002409">勝軍</persName>比量<ptr target="#n1121"/>，隨<lb
ed="T" n="0748b05"/>難應變，辭不可屈。<persName key="A009918">維摩</persName>曰：「後生可畏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1132"/>，契經<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1122"/><lb
ed="T" n="0748b06"/>所謂雖小不可欺也<ptr target="#n1123"/>。」遂率力請<persName key="A009905">止</persName>開講<placeName key="PL000000002384">恒<lb
ed="T" n="0748b07"/>陽</placeName>，緇素無不欽羨焉。迨<date key="j20417442042108" from-iso="+0878-01-01" to-iso="+0878-12-31">十九歲</date>，抵<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺<lb
ed="T" n="0748b08"/>山</placeName>求戒，於受前方便<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1124"/>，感<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>靈光爥身。已<lb
ed="T" n="0748b09"/>而<ptr type="glossary" target="#g493"/>歸寧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g399"/>父母及<ref type="person" target="#A009906">師</ref>，於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000000351">寺</ref>敷演。<date key="j20432052043569" from-iso="+0882-01-01" to-iso="+0882-12-31">二十三</date>往<placeName key="PL000000003794">并<lb
ed="T" n="0748b10"/>部</placeName>，習《法華經》、《百法論》。<date notBefore-iso="+0892-02-06" key="j20468932047631" notAfter-iso="+0894-02-13">景福年中</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000046498">河池</placeName>，有<lb
ed="T" n="0748b11"/>請講「因明」。後於<placeName key="PL000000042412">長安大莊嚴寺</placeName>化徒數載。<lb
ed="T" n="0748b12"/><date from-iso="+0896-01-23" key="j20483402048723" to-iso="+0897-02-09">乾寧三年</date>，進詩，<persName key="A003875">昭宗</persName>賜紫袈裟，應制<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042276">內殿</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0748b13"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000001520">本道</ref><persName key="A009919">劉仁恭</persName>者，據有<ref type="place" target="#PL000000000370">北門</ref>，控<anchor xml:id="beg0748sgsz2"/>扼<anchor xml:id="end0748sgsz2"/>蕃漢<ptr target="#n1125"/>，聞<persName key="A009905">止</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0748b14"/>之名，移書召歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000002485">故鄉</ref>。其父與<ref type="person" target="#A009906">師</ref>相次物故，<lb
ed="T" n="0748b15"/>母猶在堂，<persName key="A009905">止</persName>持盂乞食，以供甘旨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1126"/>。行誦《青<lb
ed="T" n="0748b16"/>龍疏》<ptr target="#n1127"/>三載，文徹忽有<anchor xml:id="beg0748sgsz3"/>巨<anchor xml:id="end0748sgsz3"/>蟒見于房，矯首顧<lb
ed="T" n="0748b17"/>視，似有所告。時同院僧<persName key="A000790">居曉</persName>，博物釋子也，<lb
ed="T" n="0748b18"/>且曰：「蛇則目睛不瞬，今其動乎？得非龍也？」<lb
ed="T" n="0748b19"/><persName key="A009905">止</persName>焚香祝之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009905">貧道</ref>念《青龍疏》，營齋養母，<lb
ed="T" n="0748b20"/>苟實龍神軫念，希值一檀越。」居數日，<ref type="person" target="#A000791">燕<anchor xml:id="beg0748003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>師</sic><corr>帥</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0748003"/></ref><ptr target="#n1128"/><lb
ed="T" n="0748b21"/><anchor xml:id="beg0748004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>家</sic><corr>冡</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0748004"/>子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1129"/>曰：「制勝司徒召申供養。」時<persName key="A006575">莊宗</persName>遣兵<lb
ed="T" n="0748b22"/>出<placeName key="PL000000002296">飛狐</placeName><ref target="#j20543062054835" type="date">以圍之，歷乎年載</ref>，百穀勇貴，<persName key="A009905">止</persName>頓<lb
ed="T" n="0748b23"/>釋憂懼。<anchor xml:id="beg0748sgsz4"/>未<anchor xml:id="end0748sgsz4"/>幾<placeName key="PL000000000368">燕</placeName>陷，<ref type="person" target="#A000791 #A009919">劉氏父子</ref>俘歸<placeName key="PL000000003796">晉陽</placeName>，<persName key="A009905">止</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0748b24"/>避亂<placeName key="PL000000002511">中山</placeName>，節度使<persName key="A009920">王處直</persName>素欽名譽，請於<lb
ed="T" n="0748b25"/><placeName key="PL000000002493">開元寺</placeName>安置，逐月供俸。<persName key="A009905">止</persName>著《頓漸教義鈔》<lb
ed="T" n="0748b26"/>一卷，見行于代。<date from-iso="+0928-01-31" key="j20600352060418" to-iso="+0929-02-17">天成三年戊子</date>，王師問罪，<placeName key="PL000000002511">定<lb
ed="T" n="0748b27"/>州</placeName>陷焉。招討使<persName key="A009921">王晏休</persName>得瀛王<persName key="A009922">馮道</persName>書，令尋<lb
ed="T" n="0748b28"/><persName key="A009905">止</persName>。既見，以車馬送至<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛京</placeName>，河南尹<persName key="A009923">秦<roleName>王</roleName>從<lb
ed="T" n="0748b29"/>榮</persName>優禮待<ref type="person" target="#A009905">之</ref>，奏署大師，號<persName key="A009905">文智</persName>焉。於<placeName key="PL000000023653">長壽<pb ed="T" n="0748c" xml:id="T50.2061.0748c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0748c01"/>淨土院</placeName>住持。<date key="j20622402062240" when-iso="+0934-02-13">應順元年甲午正月二十二日</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0748c02"/>忽微疾作，召弟子「助<ref type="person" target="#A009905">吾</ref>往生」，念彌陀佛，奄<lb
ed="T" n="0748c03"/>然而化。俗年七十五，僧臘五十六。<date key="j20622502062250" when-iso="+0934-02-23">閏正月二<lb
ed="T" n="0748c04"/>日</date><anchor xml:id="beg0748sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>茶</sic><corr>荼</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0748sgsz5"/>毘，收遺骨。至<date key="j20626992062699" when-iso="+0935-05-18">清泰二年四月八日</date>，建<lb
ed="T" n="0748c05"/>塔於<placeName key="PL000000023667">龍門山廣化寺</placeName>之東南隅。<persName key="A009905">止</persName>風神<ptr type="glossary" target="#g713"/>峭拔，<lb
ed="T" n="0748c06"/>戒節孤高，百家子史，經目無遺。該博<ptr type="glossary" target="#g350"/>之外，尤<lb
ed="T" n="0748c07"/>所長者，近體聲律詩也。有《贈<persName key="A009931">樊川長老</persName>詩》，<lb
ed="T" n="0748c08"/>流傳人口。在<placeName key="PL000000002511">定州</placeName>日，<placeName key="PL000000002511">中山</placeName>與<placeName key="PL000000003731">太原</placeName>互相疑<lb
ed="T" n="0748c09"/>貳，諸侯兼并，<persName key="A009920">王</persName>令方欲繼好息民，因命僧<lb
ed="T" n="0748c10"/>齋於<placeName key="PL000000002497">慶雲寺</placeName>。會有獻<anchor xml:id="beg0748005"/>白<anchor xml:id="end0748005"/>鵲者，<persName key="A009920">王</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009905">燕人</ref>詩<lb
ed="T" n="0748c11"/>客試為詠題。」<persName key="A009905">止</persName>即席而成，後句云：「不知誰<lb
ed="T" n="0748c12"/>會喃喃語，必向王前報太平。」<persName key="A009920">王</persName>欣然。詩人<lb
ed="T" n="0748c13"/><persName key="A009924">李洞</persName>者風<anchor xml:id="beg0748sgsz6"/>骨<anchor xml:id="end0748sgsz6"/>僻異，慕<persName key="A005203">賈閬仙</persName>之模式，<date notBefore-iso="+0892-02-06" key="j20468932047631" notAfter-iso="+0894-02-13">景福中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0748c14"/>在<placeName key="PL000000046498">河池</placeName>相遇，贈<persName key="A009905">止</persName>三篇。時宰相<persName key="A009925">孫<roleName>公</roleName>渥</persName>、<persName key="A009926">趙<lb
ed="T" n="0748c15"/><roleName>公</roleName>鳳</persName>、<persName key="A009927">馬<roleName>公</roleName>裔孫</persName>、<persName key="A009928">竇<roleName>學士</roleName>夢徵</persName>、<persName key="A009929">符<roleName>侍郎</roleName>蒙</persName>、<persName key="A009930">李<roleName>侍郎</roleName><lb
ed="T" n="0748c16"/>詳</persName>，皆唱<anchor xml:id="beg0748006"/>予<anchor xml:id="end0748006"/>和汝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1026"/>，塤箎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1130"/>韻諧。<persName key="A009905">止</persName>頃在<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0748c17"/>講罷，遊<placeName key="PL000000042657">終南山逍遙園</placeName>，是<persName key="A001583"><roleName>姚秦</roleName>什<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>譯經<lb
ed="T" n="0748c18"/>之地，年代寖深，鞠為茂草。且曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009905">吾</ref>為釋子，<lb
ed="T" n="0748c19"/>忍不興乎？」奏<persName key="A003875">昭宗</persName>乞重修，<ref type="person" target="#A003875">帝</ref>允，仍舊賜「草<lb
ed="T" n="0748c20"/>堂寺」額。後請<placeName key="PL000000042490">樊川</placeName><persName key="A009931">淨休禪伯</persName>聚徒談玄矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0748c21"/>及在<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛</placeName>也，講外長誦《金剛經》，不知紀極<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1131"/>。昔<lb
ed="T" n="0748c22"/>多居<placeName key="PL000000042627">終南山</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000056092">崆峒山</placeName>，故有《三山集》，詩三百五<lb
ed="T" n="0748c23"/>十篇，盛行于時。弟子<persName key="A009932">修文</persName>、<persName key="A009933">修智</persName>、<persName key="A009935">修行</persName>，微見<ref type="person" target="#A009905">師</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0748c24"/>之道焉。</p>
